# 编译Dlib

我们clone dlib的仓库

~~~bash
git clone https://github.com/davisking/dlib.git
~~~

然后在该目录执行

~~~bash
cmake -S . -B build -G "Visual Studio 17 2022" -A x64 -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
cmake --build build --config Debug

~~~
